  "ESCL AFTER SALES PAIRING": {
   "width": 9660,
   "height": 9060,
   "color": "rgb(130,125,47)",
   "labels": [
    {
     "text": "Protected Pairing : Electrical Steering Column Locked pairing in After Sales ",
     "color": "rgb(237,249,11)",
     "alignment": "2",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(64,0,64)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 0,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 9240
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "Procedure : ",
     "color": "rgb(242,245,118)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 480,
      "height": 5250,
      "width": 9210
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "2) Check that the BCM is not blank and the ESCL is blank (try to start the vehicle) and read the ESCL information \"SteeringLock Blanck/coded\"",
     "color": "rgb(242,245,118)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 1320,
      "height": 480,
      "width": 8745
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 7.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "3) Press the button \"Request ESCL pairing\"",
     "color": "rgb(242,245,118)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 180,
      "top": 1740,
      "height": 225,
      "width": 8820
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 7.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "4) Select the \"Input Data to Server\" (19 bytes) and copy it in the application \"Pairing using DDT2000\".  ",
     "color": "rgb(242,245,118)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(15,15,15)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 150,
      "top": 2040,
      "height": 285,
      "width": 8790
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 7.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "5) Complete the frames in the application and press the button \"Calcul\".Get the \"Server answer\" (16 bytes) and copy it in this screen. Then press the button \"Transmit Server Answer\" ",
     "color": "rgb(242,245,118)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 135,
      "top": 2655,
      "height": 615,
      "width": 8760
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 7.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "6) If the BCM is SA unlocked for ESCL pairing then put the Ignition OFF by removing the customer ID from the reader and then press the button \"Authorize ESCL pairing\" ",
     "color": "rgb(242,245,118)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 165,
      "top": 3870,
      "height": 885,
      "width": 8745
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 7.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "7) If the authorization to pair is ok, then insert the customer ID in the reader.If the ESCL is paired ( \"SteeringLock Blanck/coded\" = 0) the exit of the procedure is automatic.",
     "color": "rgb(242,245,118)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 180,
      "top": 4650,
      "height": 405,
      "width": 8745
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 7.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "ESCL / BCM information",
     "color": "rgb(240,236,179)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 4710,
      "top": 5820,
      "height": 1950,
      "width": 4605
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "MS Sans Serif",
      "size": 8.25,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "SA failure ",
     "color": "rgb(240,236,179)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 90,
      "top": 5820,
      "height": 1980,
      "width": 4515
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "MS Sans Serif",
      "size": 8.25,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "8) To postpone the authorization to pair the ESCL press the button below",
     "color": "rgb(242,245,118)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 180,
      "top": 5055,
      "height": 420,
      "width": 8760
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 7.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "1) You need first to connect to the application \"Pairing using DDT2000\" : https://gco.intra.renault.fr:14053/gco/ctrl/login and enter your IPN and Password. Then come back to this screen.",
     "color": "rgb(232,249,113)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(15,15,15)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 840,
      "height": 390,
      "width": 7620
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 7.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "Complete ( 11 bytes) before \"Transmit Server Answer\"",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(159,159,159)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 75,
      "top": 7875,
      "height": 480,
      "width": 6015
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Comic Sans MS",
      "size": 7.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    }
   ],
   "presend": [
    {
     "Delay": "0",
     "RequestName": "Extended Diagnostic Session"
    }
   ],
