  "ECM AFTER SALES PAIRING": {
   "width": 9780,
   "height": 9180,
   "color": "rgb(253,193,252)",
   "labels": [
    {
     "text": "Protected Pairing : Engine Control Module (ECM) pairing in After Sales ",
     "color": "rgb(207,207,207)",
     "alignment": "2",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(15,15,15)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 90,
      "top": 90,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 9450
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "Procedure : ",
     "color": "rgb(239,239,239)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 105,
      "top": 555,
      "height": 5310,
      "width": 9450
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "2) Check that the ECM is blank (try to start the vehicle) and read the ECM information \" VSC_UCH voit INJECTION vierge ou cod\u00e9e\"",
     "color": "rgb(239,239,239)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 180,
      "top": 1260,
      "height": 285,
      "width": 8775
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 7.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "3) Press the button \"Request Server ECM pairing\"",
     "color": "rgb(239,239,239)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 180,
      "top": 1605,
      "height": 300,
      "width": 8790
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 7.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "4) Select the \"Input Data to Server\" (19 bytes) and copy it in the application \"Pairing using DDT2000\".  ",
     "color": "rgb(239,239,239)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 165,
      "top": 2010,
      "height": 255,
      "width": 8775
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 7.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "5) Complete the frames in the application and press the button \"Calcul\".Get the \"Server answer\" (16 bytes) and copy it in this screen. Then press the button \"Transmit Server Answer\" ",
     "color": "rgb(239,239,239)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 135,
      "top": 2655,
      "height": 615,
      "width": 8760
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 7.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "1) You need first to connect to the application \"Pairing using DDT2000\" : https://gco.intra.renault.fr:14053/gco/ctrl/login and enter your IPN and Password. Then come back to this screen.",
     "color": "rgb(239,239,239)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 180,
      "top": 810,
      "height": 345,
      "width": 7740
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 7.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "6) If the BCM is SA unlocked for ECM pairing then put the Ignition Power Supply OFF by removing the customer ID from the reader/antitheft contactor and then press the button \"Authorize ECM pairing\" ",
     "color": "rgb(239,239,239)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 180,
      "top": 3885,
      "height": 885,
      "width": 8745
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 7.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "7) If the authorization to pair is ok, then insert the customer ID in the reader and press the START/STOP button of the vehicle or switch Ignition Power Supply ON. If the ECM is paired, the exit of the procedure is automatic",
     "color": "rgb(239,239,239)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 150,
      "top": 4740,
      "height": 405,
      "width": 8745
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 7.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "ECM / BCM information",
     "color": "rgb(240,236,179)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 4635,
      "top": 5955,
      "height": 3030,
      "width": 4905
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "MS Sans Serif",
      "size": 8.25,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "SA failure ",
     "color": "rgb(240,236,179)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 90,
      "top": 5955,
      "height": 2160,
      "width": 4485
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "MS Sans Serif",
      "size": 8.25,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "8) To postpone the authorization to pair the ECM press the button below",
     "color": "rgb(239,239,239)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 180,
      "top": 5205,
      "height": 645,
      "width": 8760
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 7.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "Complete ( 11 bytes) before \"Transmit Server Answer\"",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(159,159,159)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 60,
      "top": 8670,
      "height": 525,
      "width": 4590
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Comic Sans MS",
      "size": 7.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    }
   ],
